             was indicted for <rs id="t17770115-20-off95" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770115-20-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770115-20-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a ham, value 6 s. and 84. pounds weight of bacon, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770115-20-victim237" type="victimName">
                     John
                      Griffith
                  <interp inst="t17770115-20-victim237" type="surname" value="Griffith"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770115-20-victim237" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770115-20-victim237" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
